{"tid":2493854,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"上市3天，Coinbase內部人士集體套現！CFO清倉，CEO套現近3億美元","createTime":"2021-04-18T08:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T08:20:18.000Z","uid":9031,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c09b3bca24d3107659b579cd0183771ff394974","tid":2493854,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"據Cointelegraph消息，在Coinbase上市後不久，Coinbase CEO Brian Armstrong以三筆價格不同的交易出售了749999股，總計約2.92億美元。CFO Alesia Haas以388.73美元的價格出售了全部的255500股，總計約9932萬美元。<br />\n<br />\nCoinbase內部人士出售記錄如下：<br />\n<br />\nCEO：<br />\n<br />\n董事長兼首席執行官，10％所有者Brian Armstrong於4月14日出售了749,999股COIN股票，平均價格為389.1美元。<br />\n<br />\nCFO：<br />\n<br />\n首席財務官Alesia J Haas於4月14日出售255,500股COIN股票（保留了期權），平均價格為388.73美元。<br />\n<br />\n董事和高級職員、機構：<br />\n<br />\n風投機構Union Square Ventures於4月15日出售4,702,324股COIN股票，平均價格為386.36美元。<br />\n<br />\n董事Frederick Ernest Ehrsam Iii於4月15日賣出60,997股COIN股票，平均價格為334.75美元；除此之外，Frederick Ernest Ehrsam Iii還在同一日，賣出86,933股COIN股票，平均價格為398.65美元。<br />\n<br />\n首席會計官Jones Jennifer於4月14日賣出了11萬股COIN股票，平均價格為394.86美元。<br />\n<br />\n董事Marc L Andreessen於4月14日出售294,775股COIN股票，平均價格為381美元。"},{"pid":"1c12e1c61381db2fe5efed02d44b07ebb533f0a2","tid":2493854,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"傾瀉下來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3929c60b60af5c28ad23b80abcf7f198633f2578","tid":2493854,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"最大騙局"},{"pid":"655dac84a50c27946ea97ec58a0d867764746ea0","tid":2493854,"uid":315820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qiX74AU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqiX74AU.gif&h=4c7b0ddc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0319d26ceb1724634a961f5fe2118f2be8afc5f8","tid":2493854,"uid":93519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0